data.description: Charming 2 bedroom Bungalow on a cul-de-sac that dead ends into a beautiful park! This home features a lot of it's original Charm! Living room, dining and bedrooms features beautiful hardwood floors, recessed lighting throughout. Kitchen features breakfast nook, large pantry with new counter tops , double stainless steel sink with new stainless steel appliances and new tile flooring, bathroom updated with new vanity and fixtures. Home has been totally remodeled! Full basement with ample room for storage, 2 car detached garage fenced in back yard. Full size porch for Lazy evening relaxation. Perfect home for 1st time homeowner!
